/ 这里直接把'message'代码放过来循环输出，因为历史消息过多，否则会造成大量的 render partial
- messages.each do |m|
  - if m.user.id == current_user.id
    .panel.panel-default id="message_#{m.id}"
      .panel-body.text-right
        small = m.created_at
        br
        = m.content
        '
        |
        = link_to contact_message_path(c_user, m), remote: true, method: :delete do
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-remove-circle
  - else
    .panel.panel-default
      .panel-body
        small = m.created_at
        br
        = m.content